job.title: State Health Society, Bihar ANM Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 8853 Vacancies in Bihar
job.body:
Total vacancies:8853

Name of the Vacancies:

  • ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery)

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Diploma has been published by the State Health Society for ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery) vacancies in Bihar. If you are searching for a government job in Bihar then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery), from 01-07-2021, and till 21-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Bihar and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for UR/ EWS/ BC/ MBC (Male) category candidates is only Rs. 500/-
  • The application fee for UR/ EWS/ BC/ MBC (Female), SC/ ST (Bihar Domicile), PWD category candidates is only Rs. 250/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery)  in State Health Society, your Diploma (2 Years Full Time) in Auxiliary Nurse must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 01-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 21-07-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

State Health Society ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery) Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the location Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary as per norms

How to apply for State Health Society, Bihar ANM Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the ANM (Auxiliary Nurse Midwifery). Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of State Health Society and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by the State Health Society
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
